{"tid":13274,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［LIHKG健康台]有冇人一食早餐就肚痛","createTime":"2016-11-30T03:44:37.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T05:03:41.000Z","uid":14159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bd24269599724a63c3b0acddba9bf9a53726932c","tid":13274,"uid":14159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:44:37.000Z","msg":"自從中學開始每次一食早餐都奉旨會肚痛<br />\n多數都係食十弓"},{"pid":"d66db104d6e61d58f622ca9b1304b4b6159a9750","tid":13274,"uid":9375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:45:29.000Z","msg":"試下唔好空肚食早餐"},{"pid":"287f271378795d07e754c6a8d70f6b2a07ba3a2b","tid":13274,"uid":14159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:46:33.000Z","msg":"手快hi錯<br />\n多數都係食麥片 或者咬M記包朱古力<br />\n唔食早餐個陣就冇問題<br />\n好矛盾 又唔想唔食早餐 但係一食就痛<br />\n有冇人都好似我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"372d2dd6accff4f7b3b39d14f8e26d462a1efc77","tid":13274,"uid":14159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:47:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下唔好空肚食早餐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdc372392e007bbdd500507643dc1776655a8b3f","tid":13274,"uid":24866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:49:26.000Z","msg":"食早餐冇問題 不過睇下食乜<br />\n不過通常飲野就黎料 但係我就算知飲凍野會肚痛我都會照飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果飲奶真肯定奶野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d03dfe7f6711b2c3b7d656ff1d296d29af42cd","tid":13274,"uid":35712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:53:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試下唔好空肚食早餐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黎明教嫁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f446a0cf9b26e30b562cdcb0337128a033633e82","tid":13274,"uid":31927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:13:20.000Z","msg":"麥皮肚痛係正常架"},{"pid":"0ba640e7a4c05a3a6c1128a7b5411944d593d73f","tid":13274,"uid":31938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:16:07.000Z","msg":"我都係<br />\n唔知係唔慣定係咩"},{"pid":"9b7ceb89c14cbf3782a1542fb2f00a20a357dbc8","tid":13274,"uid":14159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:20:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>麥皮肚痛係正常架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 次次都痾喎"},{"pid":"c222d965106d6280d851278d11484d5dfe9a741d","tid":13274,"uid":39264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:23:21.000Z","msg":"題外話：我記得樓主好似3大?"},{"pid":"99e199f4f94e1d7abd2e2f63c1cc2bc8c6158e98","tid":13274,"uid":27575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:24:43.000Z","msg":"食完早餐一定要搵廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a379937d52d8e099c321f35cf212d058560d9ca8","tid":13274,"uid":44878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:38:37.000Z","msg":"同樓主一樣，食完就痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每日係屋企食完，到等小巴就黎料，一直忍到返學校，然後就衝去廁所痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n估計係我自己腸胃對麥皮麵包朱古力依類食物敏感 (例如奶或穀物成份??)<br />\n<br />\n試下食餅乾之類乾身食物做早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f41d6cc338861e749a3087ca4ab0fd61e05179e3","tid":13274,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:51:32.000Z","msg":"可能係因為食野叫返醒啲腸胃<br />\n開始消化同排洩"},{"pid":"b18f4a784120f5957937b5e5c2f057b533e08261","tid":13274,"uid":14159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T05:01:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>題外話：我記得樓主好似3大?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n新名來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d112e5ae720933b1a887e8d343a1cb5319d3377e","tid":13274,"uid":14159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T05:02:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同樓主一樣，食完就痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每日係屋企食完，到等小巴就黎料，一直忍到返學校，然後就衝去廁所痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n估計係我自己腸胃對麥皮麵包朱古力依類食物敏感 (例如奶或穀物成份??)<br />\n<br />\n試下食餅乾之類乾身食物做早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以仿效下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"978434403ad2bd77593ca364a7956dfd0d3e2ded","tid":13274,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T05:03:41.000Z","msg":"由細到大都係咁，細個腸胃仲敏感嗰陣連起身飲水都會肚痛，而家人大咗肚痛個機率少咗，但係變咗一起身個胃好乾好實，要起身後三四個鐘先有胃口食嘢"}]}